532  pitchyaw stability of a missile oscillating in roll via the second method of lyapunov   parks,pc  j ae scs 29, 1962, 874  pitchyaw stability of a missile oscillating in roll via the second method of lyapunov  the stability theory of a m lyapunov, a popular topic in the ussr, is receiving increasing attention elsewhere  this note describes lyapunov /second method/ very briefly and applies it to an aeronautical stability problem  
